OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781707674
OL,3,CRussian warship 'fired warning shot at
OL,4,Cyacht in English Channel'
OL,6,FSailors on a Russian warship fired a
OL,7,Fwarning shot at a UK-registered yacht
OL,8,Fthat came near it in the English
OL,9,FChannel, ITV News understands.
OL,11,FThe incident, which occurred around
OL,12,F11.40am on Tuesday, is understood to
OL,13,Fhave involved the Russian frigate
OL,14,FAdmiral Grigorovich in the sea between
OL,15,Fthe Isle of White and Normandy.
OL,17,FA Ministry of Defence spokesperson
OL,18,Fsaid: "We are investigating reports of
OL,19,Fan incident in the Channel."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
