PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781707674
OL,3,CRussian warship 'fired warning shot at
OL,4,Cyacht in English Channel'
OL,6,FIt is the latest sign of rising
OL,7,Ftensions between the UK and Moscow.
OL,9,FIn an operation on Sunday, Royal
OL,10,FMarine commandos and officers from the
OL,11,FNational Crime Agency (NCA) boarded
OL,12,Fthe sanctioned Russian shadow fleet
OL,13,Ftanker Smyrtos in the channel.
OL,15,FIn Tuesday's incident, a UK-registered
OL,16,Fyacht alleged that the Russian warship
OL,17,Ffired warning shots nearby at a
OL,18,Fdistance of approximately 500 yards
OL,19,F(457 metres).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
