FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781707674
OL,3,CRussian warship 'fired warning shot at
OL,4,Cyacht in English Channel'
OL,6,FThe shots were fired around 20
OL,7,Fnautical miles south of the Isle of
OL,8,FWight, outside UK territorial waters
OL,9,Fand caused no injuries or damage.
OL,11,FRussian warships passing through the
OL,12,FEnglish Channel are routinely shadowed
OL,13,Fby the Royal Navy, with offshore
OL,14,Fpatrol vessel HMS Mersey monitoring
OL,15,Fthe Admiral Grigorovich on Tuesday.
OL,17,FA seaboat from HMS Tyne, another
OL,18,Fpatrol vessel, was sent to the yacht
OL,19,Fto gather details and check on the
OL,20,Fsafety of the crew.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
